{"type": "article", "id": 30291, "title": "模块型盆栽架", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-28T23:01:06Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 127, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160728230640LYrqbeNVviGTluPz.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>想用花草来装饰墙面？如果你希望打造出独一无二的风格，最好的选择或许是当下流行的模块式收纳架。这组几何形盆栽架是建筑师 Luisa 和 Lilian <a href=\"http://www.luisaelilianparrado.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Parrado</a> 两姐妹的作品，仅由纤细的金属管以及混凝土搁板构成，没有其他额外的装饰。这种极简的风格搭配绿色植物带给人一种随性不做作的感觉，适用于各种不同的环境。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160728232543Zh2JD5VPiEABu4z7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160728232532TucI75otEYGCQBU8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.688333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160728232532Z3VkiorC2twP5apG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160728232532RHuesTZfxiMrQGmL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}